name: Michel Vaillant - Spionage - Der Mann von Lissabon

description: Novak takes on a seductive new client with a most unusual claim... her dreams have brought her information about murders that have not yet occurred. Including her own. Even as they discuss the case, the killer is setting up his next victim. This miniseries features art by YILDIRAY CINAR, artist on Teen Titans' Ravager and Noble Causes.
name: Beautiful Dreamer Book One

description: Jon Novak has been many things in his many lifetimes... mercenary, assassin, soldier, sailor, spy... and now he uses all the skills and experience he's acquired to help those in trouble. Sometimes for a fee, sometimes because no one else will. In addition to his many skills, he brings to the table something more. A terrible gift. A wonderful curse. Coming in contact with fresh human blood... absorbing it... allows him to take the form of that person. As with all such gifts, it comes with a price.

name: Schwitz und Krampf - jetzt machen wir Dampf!

description: Jon Novak's latest case is not going well, a killer stalks his city and he's staying just a half step ahead. Chasing after clues from his client's prophetic dreams brings Novak closer than he can imagine to the psychotic slasher. Also in this issue: a brief look back at Novak's first meeting with his assistant Heather.
name: Beautiful Dreamer Book Two

description: A madman is killing psychics and Jon Novak is hot on his trail. But when he finally catches up to him... will he survive the encounter? And if he's not there, who will rescue Heather from the clutches of a killer? Also in this issue: a brief peek inside Novak's subconscious revealing tragic facts about his past of which even he is not aware.
name: Beautiful Dreamer Book Three
